slightly aware of these jugs on the side of my face, these jug angles.

97
00:10:44,717 --> 00:10:51,049
And you can imagine, if you had the ears the size of an elephant, then you'd be aware of it.

98
00:10:51,129 --> 00:10:53,475
It would affect your self-esteem, probably.

99
